---
import "../styles/global.css";

const seo = {
  title: "Privacy Policy | Greenlight Software LLC",
  description:
    "Privacy policy for Greenlight Software LLC and the Greenlight Approvals product covering data collection, usage, and rights.",
};

const lastUpdated = "February 12, 2026";
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width" />
    <title>{seo.title}</title>
    <meta name="description" content={seo.description} />
    <link rel="icon" href="/favicon.ico" />
    <style>
      .policy-shell {
        width: min(900px, calc(100% - 2.5rem));
        margin: 3rem auto 5rem;
        background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.02);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.1);
        border-radius: 24px;
        padding: clamp(1.5rem, 4vw, 3rem);
        box-shadow: 0 40px 120px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.35);
      }

      .policy-shell h1,
      .policy-shell h2 {
        margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
      }

      .policy-shell p,
      .policy-shell li {
        color: #cdd5e0;
        line-height: 1.7;
      }

      .policy-shell ul {
        margin-left: 1.2rem;
        margin-bottom: 1.25rem;
        list-style: disc;
      }

      .divider {
        border: none;
        border-top: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.08);
        margin: 1.5rem 0;
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <header class="site-header" id="top">
      <nav class="nav">
        <a href="/" class="brand">
          <svg class="logo-mark" viewBox="0 0 120 120" role="img" aria-label="Greenlight Approvals logo">
            <defs>
              <linearGradient id="logoGradientPrivacy" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="100%">
                <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#6C63FF" />
                <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#0FB59B" />
              </linearGradient>
            </defs>
            <circle cx="60" cy="60" r="54" fill="url(#logoGradientPrivacy)" />
            <path
              d="M44 61.5L58.2 75.7 82 48.5"
              fill="none"
              stroke="#FFFFFF"
              stroke-width="12"
              stroke-linecap="round"
              stroke-linejoin="round"
            />
          </svg>
          <span>Greenlight Approvals</span>
        </a>
        <div class="nav-links">
          <a href="/#features">Product</a>
          <a href="/#pricing">Pricing</a>
          <a href="/#contact">Contact</a>
        </div>
        <a class="cta ghost" href="/#contact">Book a Demo</a>
      </nav>
    </header>
    <main class="policy-shell">
      <p class="eyebrow">Greenlight Software LLC</p>
      <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
      <p>Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>

      <hr class="divider" />

      <h2>1. Who We Are</h2>
      <p>
        Greenlight Software LLC ("we," "our," or "us") is a limited-liability company registered in Wyoming, USA. We build Greenlight Approvals and related services that integrate with NetSuite and other ERP platforms.
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>About Greenlight Approvals:</strong> Greenlight Approvals is a NetSuite-native application that provides multi-step approval workflows, budget enforcement, and compliance controls for NetSuite users. The software runs natively within NetSuite and provides approval routing, audit logging, and budget intelligence features.
      </p>
      <p>
        Questions? Contact us at <a href="mailto:hello@greenlightapprovals.io">hello@greenlightapprovals.io</a>
        or Greenlight Software LLC, Cheyenne, WY 82001, USA. EU/EEA residents can rely on us as the data controller under
        the GDPR.
      </p>

      <hr class="divider" />

      <h2>2. Information We Collect</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Contact details (name, email, company, title, phone).</li>
        <li>Form submissions (demo requests, support tickets, onboarding forms).</li>
        <li>Usage data (IP address, browser type, pages visited, analytics metrics).</li>
        <li>Marketing preferences (opt-in status, engagement).</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>3. How We Use Information</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Respond to inquiries, demo requests, and support conversations.</li>
        <li>Deliver and maintain our products and related services.</li>
        <li>Send product news or marketing updates when you opt in.</li>
        <li>Improve security, performance, and overall experience.</li>
        <li>Comply with legal or regulatory obligations.</li>
      </ul>
      <p>We do not sell or rent personal data to third parties.</p>

      <hr class="divider" />

      <h2>4. Legal Basis (EU/EEA)</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Contractual necessity for services you request.</li>
        <li>Consent for marketing communications.</li>
        <li>Legitimate interests (improving and securing our services).</li>
        <li>Legal obligations when applicable.</li>
      </ul>

      <h2>5. Data Storage & Processing</h2>
      <p>
        We use trusted sub-processors such as HubSpot (CRM/marketing), Google (email, storage, analytics), and other
        providers required to deliver our services. These vendors participate in the EU–U.S. Data Privacy Framework or
        other lawful transfer mechanisms.
      </p>
      <p>
        <strong>NetSuite Data:</strong> Greenlight Approvals operates natively within your NetSuite environment. Transaction data, approval records, and audit logs are processed and stored within NetSuite according to NetSuite's data handling practices and your NetSuite account settings. We do not extract or store your NetSuite business data outside of the NetSuite platform.
      </p>

      <h2>6. Data Retention</h2>
      <p>
        We keep personal data only as long as necessary for the purposes described above or as required by law. Marketing
        preferences are honored until you unsubscribe or withdraw consent.
      </p>

      <h2>7. Your Rights (EU/EEA)</h2>
      <ul>
        <li>Access, correct, or delete your personal data.</li>
        <li>Withdraw consent and object to processing.</li>
        <li>Request data portability.</li>
        <li>Lodge a complaint with your supervisory authority.</li>
      </ul>
      <p>Exercise these rights by contacting <a href="mailto:hello@greenlightapprovals.io">hello@greenlightapprovals.io</a>.</p>

      <h2>8. Marketing Communications</h2>
      <p>
        If you opt in, we may send occasional product updates or invitations. Each message includes an unsubscribe link,
        or you can email us directly to opt out.
      </p>

      <h2>9. Cookies & Analytics</h2>
      <p>
        Our site may use cookies and analytics tools to enhance functionality. You can adjust browser settings to refuse
        cookies, though some features may not work as intended. A standalone cookie notice may be provided.
      </p>

      <h2>10. Data Security</h2>
      <p>
        We implement encryption, access controls, and secure hosting to protect your data from unauthorized access or
        disclosure.
      </p>

      <h2>11. Changes</h2>
      <p>
        We may update this policy periodically. The latest version will always be available at
        https://greenlightapprovals.io/privacy with the “Last updated” date above.
      </p>

      <h2>12. Contact</h2>
      <p>Still have questions? Email <a href="mailto:hello@greenlightapprovals.io">hello@greenlightapprovals.io</a>.</p>
    </main>

    <footer class="footer">
      <div>
        <svg class="logo-mark" viewBox="0 0 120 120" role="img" aria-label="Greenlight Approvals logo">
          <defs>
            <linearGradient id="logoGradientFooterPrivacy" x1="0%" y1="0%" x2="100%" y2="100%">
              <stop offset="0%" stop-color="#6C63FF" />
              <stop offset="100%" stop-color="#0FB59B" />
            </linearGradient>
          </defs>
          <circle cx="60" cy="60" r="54" fill="url(#logoGradientFooterPrivacy)" />
          <path
            d="M44 61.5L58.2 75.7 82 48.5"
            fill="none"
            stroke="#FFFFFF"
            stroke-width="12"
            stroke-linecap="round"
            stroke-linejoin="round"
          />
        </svg>
        <p>© {new Date().getFullYear()} Greenlight Software LLC • Wyoming</p>
      </div>
      <div class="footer-links">
        <a href="/privacy">Privacy</a>
        <a href="/terms">Terms</a>
        <a href="/">Back to home</a>
      </div>
    </footer>
  </body>
</html>
